data.description: Great Oversized Lot, Golf Cart Garage, Wide Driveway, CBS Construction, and Whole House Generator (2022)!  This large York Model Home  features a screened courtyard that's accessible from the expansive Kitchen Area!  This property has in-house pest control, RV Hookups, Radiant Barrier, water softener, a gas line in the lanai for your BBQ grill, and great curb appeal.  Inside, you love the solar skylights, crown moldings, inside laundry room, bullnose corners, and knockdown ceiling texture.  The kitchen is one of the largest of all the Pringle Model homes!  It offers eating space, a mobile island, large pantry, 42" upper cabinets, ceramic tile, granite counters, and a large pass through to the dining room!  The primary bedroom & bathroom suite have large closets, laminate flooring, access to the Florida Room, which features acrylic windows, dual vanities, private comode, and a walk in shower.  Situated in a quiet culdesac in the gated, golf community of Royal Highlands! This 55+ HOA includes cable and internet in the monthly HOA fees!  The campus includes a full service restaurant, pro shop, driving range, fitness center and two pools.  Enjoy entertainment in the Great Hall or attend the multiple dances the community has to offer.   Courts, Crafts, Softball Field, Library and Billiards are also part of this great community.  Come see this beautiful home and active,  adult community today.  2023 HVAC & 2015 Roof.
